"returns this week as master of ceremonies after being absent the last two weeks due to illness."

comments.content: Unclear if it's actually Gita Gilmore. Article only refers to Gita. But no other Gita is known as a female impersonator. "When You See GITA The Comedian in 'Them Thar Hills,' you will split your sides with laughter"
